    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reopen driving test centres for essential workers during the second lockdown",
        "additional_details": "The government are allowing people to Continue using public transport which does not have the best hygiene in comparison to a driving instructors car which is constantly cleaned after each person has used it. I would like the government to open up test centres for \u2018essential workers again\u2019. This would also benefit other people in the long run as the waiting list for a test would decrease by a lot.",
        "background": "From our first lockdown, people considered \u2018essential workers\u2019 were allowed to continue with their tests. We are now in November lockdown number 2 and ALL tests have been cancelled.",
